:::'''Hekate:''' Do you have something to do here? If you need help, I can offer some assistance.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Just running an errand for the people beside me.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} No problem, it's already been solved.
:::'''Hekate:''' That's good... I know you're strong, but right now the black tide hasn't dissipated, and it's still extremely dangerous.
:::{{tx}}
::'''Hekate:''' If there's nothing else, you'd better return to Okhema soon.
